replies.body:
Hey,

I've hit a quick edit on your post.  There's no reason to bring a person's status on the Boards into the discussion or make implied accusations of lack of game knowledge.  If someone makes what you believe is an invalid argument, refute it with proof/facts (as the rest of your comment does) and leave any commentary about how they lack game knowledge out of it.

{{sticker:poppy-wink}}
